-- H20 Innovation Reports Termination of Joint Venture in India
-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 2013-05-28T12:45:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-28/h20-innovation-reports-termination-of-joint-venture-in-india.html
H20 Innovation, a water-treatment
company based in  Quebec City , has decided to terminate its
participation in its joint venture in India, the company said in
a news release.  The joint venture was created three years ago under the
name H2O Innovation India Ltd. and announced on Feb. 1, 2010.
Sales objectives have not been met, the company said.  H20, a membrane filtration solution provider, is now a
partner in the Rockwell Automation OEM Program, part of the
Rockwell Automation PartnerNetwork, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  